-Dany. Fuck.

642
00:52:12.066 --> 00:52:13.366
[Dany speaking Ukrainian]

643
00:52:13.466 --> 00:52:15.566
[in Ukrainian]

644
00:52:32.400 --> 00:52:33.533
-Dany.
-What?

645
00:52:33.633 --> 00:52:35.000
