662
00:54:15.500 --> 00:54:16.666
You stay right here.

663
00:54:17.833 --> 00:54:18.833
Right here.

664
00:54:24.866 --> 00:54:27.566
-[scuffling]
-[muted chatter]

665
00:54:27.666 --> 00:54:29.000
