671
00:55:10.833 --> 00:55:12.033
Shit.

672
00:55:12.900 --> 00:55:17.466
[speaking Ukrainian]

673
00:55:23.366 --> 00:55:24.400
We gotta go.

674
00:55:29.366 --> 00:55:30.800
