707
00:58:14.700 --> 00:58:16.166
What about my family?

708
00:58:17.333 --> 00:58:18.693
Thought you wanted
to get them out.

709
00:58:24.733 --> 00:58:26.466
[speaking Ukrainian]

710
00:58:55.533 --> 00:58:58.366
[distant gunfire]

711
00:59:14.166 --> 00:59:17.400
