of any foreign prisoners?

715
01:01:28.733 --> 01:01:29.866
Anything connecting Riley?

716
01:01:30.400 --> 01:01:33.666
Uh... uh. no. Nothing.

717
01:01:36.300 --> 01:01:37.833
