Connor. thank you
for coming back for us.

740
01:03:51.400 --> 01:03:53.333
But this is the wrong way
for Riley. no?

741
01:03:55.300 --> 01:03:56.300
She's. um...

742
01:03:58.866 --> 01:03:59.866
