Uh. speaking of.
how's the hunt going?

770
01:05:44.400 --> 01:05:46.800
-Any luck?
-No. No luck.

771
01:05:47.966 --> 01:05:49.376
I think that's
highly debatable. mate.

772
01:05:49.400 --> 01:05:50.640
